# Career and Investment Platform

A web-based platform developed as a final year group project that connects developers and consumers, enabling developers to showcase their applications/websites and users to explore and interact with them.

---

## Project Overview

This project is designed to build a digital platform where:

* Developers can upload and showcase their applications/websites
* Consumers can browse, explore, and evaluate available applications
* A structured system supports interaction between both user types
* Basic Machine Learning concepts are used for improving recommendations

---

## Key Features

* Developer panel to manage and showcase projects
* Consumer interface to browse applications
* Search and filter functionality
* Basic ML-based recommendation support
* Simple and user-friendly UI design

---

## Tech Stack

* Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
* UI Frameworks: Bootstrap, Tailwind CSS
* Backend: Node.js
* Concepts Used: Service-Oriented Architecture (SOA), Machine Learning

